strings.Value: "It seems your goblin ally and his tribe have been industrious – they are erecting statues to {g|Lamashtu}Lamashtu{/g}, the Mother of Beasts right outside the capital. Do... they do this with your leave?"

"It seems your goblin friend and his allies have been industrious in their latest blasphemy – they are erecting statues to {g|Lamashtu}Lamashtu{/g}, the Mother of Beasts right outside the capital. It's heresy, and it is spreading fear and panic among the people."
